snippet.title: Army Men: Sarge's War (Trailer)
snippet.description: I found this video on a channel called "tellysarmy". Pretty sure it's not legit because it has scenes from Green Rogue and such, but man is this good. Only like the end is from an actual teaser trailer I think.
